# LFS PUMF (71M0001X): ``discover`` = read monthly links from the product page + probe hist/YYYY-CSV.zip for past years (AUTO_HIST). Or list tokens: hist:2025, 2026-03, https://…
STATCAN_LABOUR_PUMF_SOURCES=discover
STATCAN_LABOUR_PUMF_PRODUCT_PAGE_URL=https://www150.statcan.gc.ca/n1/pub/71m0001x/71m0001x2021001-eng.htm
STATCAN_LABOUR_PUMF_BASE_URL=https://www150.statcan.gc.ca/n1/pub/71m0001x/2021001
